section.section:
"Computer" does not include:
A personal digital assistant device;
A computer peripheral device, including:
A mouse or other similar pointing device;
A printer; or
A detachable keyboard.

"Solid waste stream" does not include:
Hospital waste;
Rubble;
Scrap material;
Land clearing debris;
Sewage sludge; or
Waste generated by a single individual or business and disposed of in a facility dedicated solely for that entity's waste.

text.section:
"White goods" includes:
Refrigerators;
Stoves;
Washing machines;
Dryers;
Water heaters; and
Air conditioners.
